{"tid":552667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=??  高鐵工疑遭欠薪$900萬","createTime":"2018-02-06T17:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T09:42:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9e59a6dab9c9f4e35107a0d1a9217a35522a03","tid":552667,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"高鐵地盤發生勞資糾紛。現場為荃灣象山村附近的高鐵通風設施工程地盤，大批工人疑被拖欠薪金，於今午(6日)約2時發起行動，在寒風中包圍地盤靜坐，並在泥頭車車斗上掛上寫有「年關將至慘！慘！慘！」以及「港鐵監管無力」等字句的橫額，各人身前都擺有示威標語，包括「有汗出，無糧出」等。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，涉事工人主要負責城門通風樓附近的路面還原及復修工程。有工人聲稱，通風設施工程已接近竣工，但地盤內有近70名工友，<span style=\"color: red;\">疑遭判頭拖欠薪金長達8個月</span>，涉款達900萬港元。工友向大判了解，對方曾提及並聲稱「因港鐵公司未畀錢」，其後一直沒有支薪的消息，因此工友們發起行動，工人管工亦已部署明早再展開行動討薪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180206/bkn-20180206210124665-0206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180206%2Fbkn-20180206210124665-0206_00822_001.html&d=8QKeduE8D59wrLrvr8TMksmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=fe995f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180206/bkn-20180206210124665-0206_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e128c8d6554cccdd3e24f1c5eca70c9772e60b2d","tid":552667,"uid":17641,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:32:11.000Z","msg":"為了國家發展不應該跟國家計較薪水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8961230faaf31bc4aa7e01b74a47e149e6be647","tid":552667,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:55:07.000Z","msg":"返工=危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nReal slave ,no pay"},{"pid":"a1fb7d03e528a51aaf8d8592764176ea7edbb6b0","tid":552667,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"連登地盤佬最興講幾錢幾錢一工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0b58e31bb18de68f520431b7879d5ed530007f","tid":552667,"uid":46527,"like":5,"dislike":